{
  "texts": [
    "A major challenge lies in the limited transparency of many deep learning models.",
    "Their opaque decision-making processes can make it difficult to predict how they will perform in unfamiliar contexts.",
    "This highlights the importance of using interpretable and verifiable modeling techniques when developing AIbased sensory innovations.",
    "In addition, there is a growing need for cultural sensitivity in AI-driven sensory applications.",
    "Taste and smell are deeply embedded in cultural practices and individual identities."
  ]
}